  "description": "A breathtaking landscape photograph capturing a vibrant sunset over a coastal city. The sky is dominated by a striking pattern of altocumulus undulatus clouds, arranged in long, parallel waves, radiating from a hazy golden sun. Below, a sprawling urban area meets the tranquil waters of a bay or sea. In the foreground, a dark, hilly landscape covered with dense vegetation provides a natural frame for the panoramic view. The city lights begin to twinkle as dusk settles. The composition creates a sense of depth and scale, contrasting the vastness of the sky with the compact city below.",
